fi.arithmeticvisualizer.logic.nodes

Class BinaryNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.arithmeticvisualizer.logic.nodes.Node
      • fi.arithmeticvisualizer.logic.nodes.BinaryNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdditionNode, LeftScalarMultiplicationNode, MatrixMultiplicationNode, RightScalarMultiplicationNode, SubtractionNode

    public abstract class BinaryNode
extends Node
    A BinaryNode is a Node that performs an operation on two operands. The abstract class is extended by AdditionNode, SubtractionNode and MultiplicationNode.
